<doc id="29086" wikidata="Q54800709" url="?curid=29086" title="Sansad">
<text>Sansad or Sangsad is the word for &quot;Assembly&quot;, association, council or &quot;Parliament&quot; in several Indo-Aryan languages, derived from a Sanskrit root. It may also mean:
== National parliament ==
===Bangladesh===
