===Records set===
The following records were set or tied in Super Bowl V, according to the official NFL.com boxscore, the 2016 NFL Record &amp; Fact Book and the ProFootball reference.com game summary. Some records have to meet a required minimum number of attempts in order to be recognized. The minimums are shown (in parentheses).

Turnovers are defined as the number of times losing the ball on interceptions and fumbles.


